---
title: Pan-Fried Pork & Creamy All-American Sauce with Veggies & Potato Mash
description: It’s pork for dinner tonight and this recipe won’t disappoint. Pan-fry the pork to get that golden coating and drizzle over an
All-American spice blend sauce with a creamy texture. Grab a helping of buttered mashed potatoes and veggies to round out the
meal and give it that classic combo hit.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

